name: Unidentified_Black_Sun_member_2
content: A Falleen individual was a member of the Black Sun criminal syndicate during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the Falleen, alongside another Falleen confronted a gorgmonger in Ord Mantell City on the planet Ord Mantell. The Falleen took a gorg and ate it whilst their colleague spoke with the gorgmonger about their business operating without having paid Black Sun protection fees. The Falleen found the gorg nice to eat, and informed their colleague that they should try one. The two Black Sun members were then approached by members of the Unbroken Clan, who declared that Ord Mantell now belonged to them before they killed the two Falleen.
